title: Calphalon Self Sharpening Cutlery with SharpIN
description: Calphalon Self Sharpening Cutlery with SharpIN
transcripts:
[MUSIC PLAYING] Calphalon self-sharpening cutlery features SharpIN technology, which keeps knives sharp for a lifetime. Innovative Calphalon cutlery blocks have built in ceramic sharpeners that automatically sharpen knives every time you take them out and put them back into the block. With SharpIN technology, knives are at peak sharpness every time you use them. 

Now tasks such as slicing, chopping, and dicing, are effortless. With freshly sharpened knives whenever you need them, Calphalon self-sharpening cutlery is available in classic, contemporary, and precision lines, each with their own premium knife design and block style. 

Home cooks and professionals know that sharp knives are essential to every kitchen. And Calphalon SharpIN technology delivers by automatically sharpening with each use. Calphalon self-sharpening cutlery with SharpIN technology. Stay sharp for a lifetime. 

[MUSIC PLAYING]
